Can your family afford a 22% tax hike?

@POTUS' One Big Beautiful Bill will STOP that from taking place. 

It will save the average American family $1,700 and lock in and boost the doubled Child Tax Credit for more than 40 million families.

Selfridge ANGB is vital to our national defense and Michigan’s economic strength.

@POTUS is focused on restoring our military’s lethal edge, and our crown jewel of #MI10, Selfridge, is poised to meet the challenge.

I’m focused on aligning efforts with President Trump and @SecDef to work to secure a new fighter mission for Selfridge.
